VERDICT: G-L5-RECALL-LIVE and the scaled-prompt receipt are NOT REPRODUCIBLE on the current
stack. Selection is stable; DELIVERY OBEDIENCE on paraphrase queries is fragile across builds/
days despite pinned code+data+weights+driver. Within-run deterministic, cross-run divergent =>
the un-pinned surface is the float prefill/logit path feeding the thin obey-vs-parametric margin
(the S1 FP-reorder lesson, now on answer-content instead of coherence).

